      <title>中国内地与香港拓宽投融资联系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/china-hong-kong-broaden-investment-and-financing-links</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港宣布多项措施深化金融联系——包括促进内地房地产购买和扩大财富通计划——与中国进一步融合，使这座城市与内地进一步融合。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/china-hong-kong-broaden-investment-and-financing-links</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 10:45:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
