      <title>尼日利亚央行行长称奈拉“被低估”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/nigeria-s-cardoso-sees-inflation-cooling-says-ngn-usd-undervalued</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚央行行长奥拉耶米·卡多佐(Olayemi Cardoso)表示，今年通胀将会放缓，并在自去年11月以来首次对经济发表公开评论时称该国奈拉货币“被低估”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/nigeria-s-cardoso-sees-inflation-cooling-says-ngn-usd-undervalued</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 10:31:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
