    </item>
    <item>
      <title>服务业下滑，欧元区制造业好于预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-24/euro-area-manufacturing-beats-estimates-as-services-fall-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三数据显示，标普全球采购经理人指数微升至 47.9，欧元区 1 月份私营部门活动连续第八个月萎缩。制造业跃升至 10 个月高点，而服务业则超出分析师预期，跌至 48.4。贾娜·兰多 (Jana Randow) 接受彭博电视台报道。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-24/euro-area-manufacturing-beats-estimates-as-services-fall-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 09:49:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国通过允许银行保留较小的准备金来刺激经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/pboc-will-cut-rrr-for-banks-in-early-february-governor-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国表示将在两周内降低银行存款准备金率，并暗示将采取更多支持措施，这一异常提前的披露表明习近平主席政府提振经济和阻止 6 万亿美元股市暴跌的紧迫性越来越大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/pboc-will-cut-rrr-for-banks-in-early-february-governor-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 07:43:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚棕榈油收成因外籍工人流动而增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/palm-oil-harvest-in-malaysia-gets-boost-from-foreign-worker-move</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚棕榈油协会首席执行官 Joseph Tek 表示，在政府允许种植园雇用外国工人后，第二大供应国马来西亚的棕榈油产量今年可能会增长 5%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/palm-oil-harvest-in-malaysia-gets-boost-from-foreign-worker-move</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 04:19:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>金属交易一系列丑闻的背后是什么？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-09-01/why-are-there-so-many-scandals-in-metals-trading-and-what-s-being-done</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一系列丑闻震动了金属市场，并重新唤起了人们对在工业经济中发挥关键作用的仓储和运输网络脆弱性的担忧。最新的事件让一些世界上最负盛名的贸易公司陷入困境，并暴露了与伦敦金属交易所相关的仓库的监管缺陷——全球基本金属基准期货市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-09-01/why-are-there-so-many-scandals-in-metals-trading-and-what-s-being-done</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Sep 2023 09:47:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
